Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:05.97,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:08.68,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:13.86,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:18.99,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:31.71,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:40.17,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:52.06,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.31,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:58.07,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:01:02.95,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:08.45,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:17.75,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:37.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:39.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's L?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's different from what I imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:47.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Detective Superintendent Yagami\Nof the National Police Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:49.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:50.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:51.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:52.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ukita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:55.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:57.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These five are our current...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:58.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:01:59.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:01.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:06.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Soichiro Yagami,\Nif I were Kira you would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:14.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You already know that all Kira needs\Na face and a name, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:17.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't give out\Nyour name so carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:19.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's value our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about him needing a face,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:27.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I haven't heard anything\Nabout him needing a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:33.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Criminals whose names were unknown or\Nwhose names were broadcast incorrectly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:35.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,were all spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:38.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was discussed at\Ntask force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:41.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not stand around and chat,\Nplease come right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:45.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please turn off all cell phones, laptops,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:48.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and other electronic devices and\Nplace them on that table.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:53.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, do you think that we'd make calls\Non our cell phones
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:55.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and leak our information to the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:56.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know he's cautious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:03.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't tell if he trusts us or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:09.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stand it when people's\Ncell phones go off when I'm talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:11.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me start by saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:16.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not take any notes on anything\Nwe say at this headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep all of it in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, sit wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:22.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, L...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:50.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you refer to me from now on\NI wish to be called Ryuzaki, not L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then, Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:57.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that a face and\Na name are needed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:01.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then couldn't we cut down the number\Nof victims by censoring crime reports?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, then ordinary people\Nwould be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:06.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's childish and hates to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:12.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Childish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And hates to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:20.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also childish and hate to lose...\NThat's why I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:25.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you explain that a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:30.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I declared war against\NKira on television...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:35.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, we thought that\NKira was only after criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:38.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't hesitate to kill my double.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, as soon as I said\Nhe was hiding in the Kanto region...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:46.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He started drawing most of his victims\Nfrom Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:48.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as if to say, "So what if I am?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:56.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's met each of my challenges\Nwithout flinching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:02.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if we tried to use media restrictions to\Nhide criminals from someone like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:03.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you won't give me your criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:10.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"then I'll kill those who've committed\Nlighter crimes or even the innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:15.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The whole world is my hostage!\NI'm not the evil one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:19.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Those who oppose me\Nand hide evil-doers are!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how Kira's mind works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of the mass media,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:28.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,let's think of ways we can\Nuse it to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:29.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:31.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"U.S. furious over deaths of FBI agents."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira's antics have angered\Nthe whole world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:41.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"the leading nations send a total\Nof 1,500 investigators into Japan."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be different from\Nhis recent experience with the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:48.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He would begin to see everyone\Nas a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:53.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When he's at his limit,\Nit should cause some sort of response.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:06:00.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,1,500 instead of the\Nactual group of seven, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:04.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And unlike those FBI agents,\Nthey don't exist and they can't be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This could work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:10.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll tell you my thoughts\Non the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira works alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:18.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was accessing inside information\Nfrom the investigation before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:21.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you believe he's working alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:22.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:25.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's listen to Ryuzaki's\Nentire theory first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira needs a name and face to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:31.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To a certain degree, he can even\Ncontrol the victim's time of death
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the actions the victim\Ntakes before his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With all of that in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen closely to the following.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On December 14,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:48.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,twelve FBI agents\Nentered Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,December 19...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:55.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira began using prisoners\Nto conduct tests
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,concerning actions a victim\Ncan take before death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nduring just this five-day period,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:05.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira became aware of the FBI's presence\Nand felt threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he didn't know\Ntheir faces or names,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to eliminate all of the FBI agents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:15.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He had to see how far\Nhe could control the deaths of his victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, on December 27...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After making sure the FBI agents\Nreceived the file
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:25.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with all the names and faces\Nof the other agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I succeeded in killing all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:31.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is nearly impossible to\Nfigure out whose files Kira saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:33.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let anyone know that\NI came into contact with Raye Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:41.68,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(321,316)}Bus
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:46.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're not using\Nthe Death Note today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you studying for the entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use practicing\Nfor those at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:59.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked the most between\NDecember 19 and 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:05.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Within this time, 23 people died\Nof heart attacks as we all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:09.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all wanted criminals,\Nex-convicts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And people who were\Nsuspected of crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:15.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People obviously different\Nfrom those Kira usually targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:17.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:21.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that in order to\Nkill the FBI agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:24.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he needed to control those\Nwith even lesser crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:29.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed 23 people,\Nso we couldn't tell who he used.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He actually probably only used a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He left eight days after the tests
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:39.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to allow the FBI to gather\Ninformation on other suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to draw attention\Naway from himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:44.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I suspect that Kira\Nwas one of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:50.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who was being investigated by the FBI\Nbetween the 14th and the 19th.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is data from the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:57.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It contains other important information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take these out\Nof this room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:01.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we have this much information,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:06.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,our small group can do more\Nthan enough on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:09.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split into two groups.\NOne will trace the FBI agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the other will research\Nthose who had heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:15.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only a few people who\Nwere able to get info from headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:19.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,whom the FBI were investigating\Nduring their first five days!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, does anyone have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:27.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Ryuzaki,\NI have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said earlier that you hate to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've shown us your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:37.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean that you've\Nalready lost to Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:38.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I've shown my face
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:44.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and that I've sacrificed\Ntwelve FBI agents are both losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will win in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time\NI've laid my life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:54.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show Kira that\Nwe're willing to risk our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because justice will definitely prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:01.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice will prevail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:06.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:11.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first saw him,\NI was suspicious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:12.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:18.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, in order to make sure\NKira isn't among us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to talk to each of\Nyou individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he doesn't trust us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:32.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira's been gathering information\Nfrom headquarters from the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,chances are high that\Nhe's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:36.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we've stayed on the case,\Nwe've seen Ryuzaki's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:41.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this is a risk, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have been going well so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:50.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had one more thing,\Njust one more decisive clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was just one thing I missed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:56.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one piece of evidence\Nthat would come to light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:59.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It could cost me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Just one thing...\N- Just one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish your studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:28.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:29.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:31.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't anything I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:34.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My biggest gamble was\Nthe bus-jacking incident, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is impossible to connect it with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:40.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police and L don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:44.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that Kira can kill people with\Nmeans other than heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:50.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if anyone were to discover that fact,\Nit would be a huge problem for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:56.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's been pulling overnighters.\NHe needs clean clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to give this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:00.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised I'd go to the first New Year's\NShrine Visit with my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:02.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:03.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could use a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:04.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:10.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that you can\Nspy on the Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only be able to go as far as\Nthe receptionist's desk though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:19.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're bringing a page?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An outing to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I've been doing\Nthis when I go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:25.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:35.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raye said that he was going to\Ngo to Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On that same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:42.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there were four heart attacks\Nin the Shinjuku area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bus-jacker Dies After\NBeing Hit By Car\NAnd... a bus-jacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:48.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:50.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira can...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.62,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(181,109)\fad(667,375)}National Police\NAgency and\NNational Public\NSafety Commission
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,kill by means other than heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The number you have just dialed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual for Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:12.01,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(276,110)}National Police\NAgency and\NNational Public\NSafety Commission
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:12.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's at an important meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:19.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I must speak directly to someone\Nfrom the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you already,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:25.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no one in\Nthe Kira Task Force Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one in the headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:31.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's phone is off...\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way I can contact them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something very important\Nrelating to the Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira investigation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll try to call their headquarters\Nonce more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:48.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Detective Superintendent\NSoichiro Yagami's son, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought my father's change of clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:53.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it doesn't look like he's here,\Ncould you hold on these for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Light, I haven't seen you\Naround in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...sorry.\NUmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:02.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? We solved that\Ninsurance murder with your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the receptionist then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:07.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just write my name here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:14.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that you're\Ngoing to help the Kira case, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:15.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If all goes well,\NI may be able to beat L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat L?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's at their headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please trust me on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to give them\Nyour message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:29.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:30.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:34.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is leading\Nthe Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to leave\Na message with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His cell phone is off,\Nso I can't tell him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're probably busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:45.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of FBI agents were killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:48.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and a lot of detectives quit the case\Nbecause they were afraid of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, you shouldn't be\Ntelling civilians that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:55.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People are already talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this person is trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:14:59.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell by looking at her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a very wise and careful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:05.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard about the FBI incident,\Nand you figured out that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:08.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a problem within\Nthe Japanese police force itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:12.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you want to speak\Ndirectly to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably get a call\Nfrom my father
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,once he gets the message\NI left on his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk directly to him at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:26.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:27.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give you my father's\Ncell phone number,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:33.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can use my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:38.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's no use if\Nyou don't trust both of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:42.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that cheery attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've managed to lead\Nher along well, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:54.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To involve yourself in the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:58.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:01.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that Kira is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:08.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, may I ask what your name is?\NMy name is Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:12.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light as in the character for "moon,"\Nand Yagami as in "night god."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:13.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strange name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shoko Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:18.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko for "shining child,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and Maki as in "space" and "tree."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Maki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:28.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Maki, I think that Kira's powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:32.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,enable him to control\Nhis victims before he kills them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought so too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:37.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I was thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:40.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira can control the actions\Nof a person before death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:41.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:44.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If my analysis is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:48.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira can also kill people by\Nmeans other than heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:55.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone's noticed yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:59.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think this is what's\Ngoing to help us catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:03.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't even thought about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira would make sure not to\Ngive his victims heart attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:09.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when he's intent on hiding a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:10.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:13.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I know may have met Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:14.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Met Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:21.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting Kira is definitely something
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:23.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that the police would have\Na hard time believing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:24.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:26.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I have to explain it\Nin detail to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:29.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,someone from the\Ntask force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:33.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't it be better if\Nthat person spoke to them instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is no longer alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:41.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was one of the FBI agents\Nwho came to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:46.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An FBI agent who met Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:48.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also my fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he witnessed\Na bus-jacking incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:58.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably met Kira\Non that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raye Penber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:07.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:08.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry your fiancé's passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:16.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...what makes you think\Nhe met Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:20.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight days after the bus-jacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:24.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He died, along with\Nthe other FBI agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:30.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That bus-jacker robbed\Na bank two days earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He died in an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,an unusual and rare set of events...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:38.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that Kira set up\Nthe bus-jacking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:42.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to steal information from my fiancé...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:48.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to kill the FBI agents\Nwho had come to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:52.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus-jacker died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:56.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, heart attacks aren't\Nthe only way that Kira can kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus-jacker didn't die\Nof a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:15.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you think that Kira\Ncan kill by means other than heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:16.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:20.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's a bit of a leap...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:22.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:27.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but think that the bus-jacker\Nwas being controlled by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:28.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:30.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:33.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the bus-jacking ever since\Nmy fiancé told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him about it more\Nwhen he was relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:41.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't name names,\Nbut he did tell me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:46.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That he reluctantly showed\Nhis FBI ID to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a top-secret investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:54.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that the FBI was hiding from\Nthe Japanese police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:57.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't supposed to show his ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:20:03.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So whoever saw his ID was the one\Nwho let slip that the FBI was in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She really knows what\Nshe's talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:09.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So this would be the oversight\Nthat Light was worrying about!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:11.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:15.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a conclusion you came to\Nwith your singular knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:17.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and your desire to avenge your fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe that Kira can\Nmurder his victims
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by means other than by heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:22.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:23.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some amazing deductive skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't deny you have\Npersonal interests in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your argument seems a bit forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:33.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...this theory is definitely\Nworth investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your testimony will be\Nvery important to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:37.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:42.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If what you said is correct,\NKira should be caught soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:49.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira was the one your fiancé\Nshowed his ID to on that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:04.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If this woman had spoken\Nto the police before she met me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:06.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that a god other\Nthan a Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:12.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:28.75,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:34.13,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:43.14,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:49.52,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:54.11,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:59.83,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:07.25,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:12.46,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:23.22,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:29.02,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:44.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see how\Nthis woman dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:47.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't be caught\Nfollowing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:51.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry to your death.
